---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: About — Verdandi Weaver
description: About Sara Leidelmeijer and the body of work that is Verdandi Weaver.
permalink: /about.html
---

{% set about = collections.about | first %}
{% if about %}{% set d = about.data %}{% endif %}

<section class="hero container fade-up">
  <p class="t-eyebrow hero__eyebrow">About</p>
  <h1 class="t-h1 hero__title t-balance">{{ d.hero_title if d else "A space for soul presence" }}</h1>
</section>

<section class="section fade-up"><div class="container narrow stack-lg">

  {% if d and d.image %}
    <div class="figure" style="aspect-ratio: 4/3">
      <img src="{{ d.image }}" alt="Sara Leidelmeijer" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);">
    </div>
  {% else %}
    <div class="figure" style="aspect-ratio: 4/3"><div class="placeholder" style="aspect-ratio: 4/3">[ portrait — Sara Leidelmeijer ]</div></div>
  {% endif %}

  <p class="t-lead t-pretty">{{ d.lead if d else "Verdandi Weaver is the body of work of <strong>Sara Leidelmeijer</strong> — a writer, systemic thinker, and bridge-builder between science, spirit, nervous systems, and relational life." | safe }}</p>

  <h2 class="t-h3">What this work is</h2>
  <p class="t-body t-pretty">{{ d.what_it_is if d else "A grounded approach to being human — including the soul, the nervous system, the body, the mind, identity, relationships, and the world they all live inside. A return rather than an escape." }}</p>

  <h2 class="t-h3">What it isn't</h2>
  <p class="t-body t-pretty">{{ d.what_it_isnt if d else "Not a transcendence project. Not a productivity stack. Not a fix. Wholeness begins when nothing in you is left out — including your tired parts, your doubt, your softness, and your quiet refusal." }}</p>

  <h2 class="t-h3">How it's offered</h2>
  <p class="t-body t-pretty">{{ d.how_offered if d else "Through books, slow essays, gentle self-scans, visual frameworks, and — over time — circles and courses. Free where it can be, sustaining where it needs to be." }}</p>

  <span class="rule"></span>

  {% if d and d.pull %}
    <p class="pull">{{ d.pull }}</p>
  {% else %}
    <p class="pull">You don't awaken out of being human. <em>You awaken into it.</em></p>
  {% endif %}

  {% if d and d.footer_note %}
    <p class="t-meta center-text">{{ d.footer_note }}</p>
  {% else %}
    <p class="t-meta center-text">Working from Sweden · in English &amp; Swedish.</p>
  {% endif %}

</div></section>
